snippet: Two men apprehended in a raid in a Sydney suburb have been charged with planning an act of terrorism and other offenses, officials said.
abstract: Australian police arrest two men in Sydney suburb on suspicion of intent to carry out imminent terrorist attack.
lead_paragraph: Two men apprehended in a raid in a Sydney suburb have been charged with planning an act of terrorism and other offenses, officials said.

headline.main: Australia Arrests 2 on Suspicion of Plotting ‘Imminent’ Attack
